Top 100 General Managers of the World by Luxury Lifestyle Awards', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/marcelbangkok', 'marcelbangkok', $${"about": "A results-driven, innovative management professional with 18 years' experience as Hotel/Resort General Manager. Strong background in sales and marketing, rooms division, and food and beverage, with a keen eye for detail. An individual who promotes a memorable, lasting experience by exceeding guest expectations. Driving strong, profitable growth while reducing costs, improving quality, and continuously improving returns to both owners and partners. A hands-on, led-by-example approach to management chic\n\nKey Achievements\n\nGeneral Manager with experience in Thailand, the Maldives, and China across large city hotels to Luxury small resorts, and apartments.\nPre-opening of Two City Hotels in China and One Resort in Thailand, plus the Newly Opened Ifuru in the Maldives\nStrong Background in rebinding resorts and Hotels\nA proven track record in sales and marketing, hotel division, and food and beverage, coming from owning Michelin Star Restaurants in Sydney and Switzerland\nGM of Hotels and Resorts from 150 Keys to 1100 Keys, from 2 Restaurants to 24 Restaurants and Bars, plus nightclubs \nMy collaborative nature is one of my most substantial assets, and I enjoy working in groups. By inspiring and working alongside team members, I achieved the results of the projects I directed. Due to my creativity, open-mindedness, attention to detail, and flexibility, I have increased productivity by 10% at Marco Polo Hotels over the past five years.  \nMy greatest strength is my ability to solve problems quickly and efficiently. Because I can view situations from multiple perspectives, I am uniquely qualified to complete my work effectively, even in challenging circumstances. Communicating effectively comes more easily to me because I can solve problems. As much as I enjoy speaking with junior team members, I feel equally comfortable with senior executives. My ability to see both sides of an issue will make me a valuable member of your team.  \nCreativity, Determination, Trustworthiness, and Enthusiasm.  \nA proven track record of leadership and teamwork in the hotel and group industry  \nAward-winning General Manager from Thailand and China", "addressCountryOnly": "Thailand", "addressWithCountry": "Bangkok Metropolitan Area, Thailand", "addressWithoutCountry": "Bangkok Metropolitan Area", "backgroundPic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5616AQH2HAJvjgfnng/profile-displaybackgroundimage-shrink_350_1400/B56ZUPBlJiGsAY-/0/1739713834672?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=0gucTrjT2eM9dwWvszCclW_5YErSVRPUSCDrF1thpWQ", "companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "companyLinkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/ifuru-island-maldives/", "companyName": "Ifuru Island Maldives", "companySize": "51-200", "companyWebsite": "https://ifuruisland.com/", "connections": "4086", "creatorWebsite/0/category": "COMPANY", "creatorWebsite/0/url": "https://www.chatrium.com/grandbangkok", "creatorWebsite/1/category": "PORTFOLIO", "creatorWebsite/1/url": "http://www.pata-thailand.org/", "currentJobDuration": "2 yrs 9 mos", "currentJobDurationInYrs": "2.75", "educations/0/companyId": "17197", "educations/0/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/school/assumption-university/", "educations/0/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:17197", "educations/0/description": "KPI Thinking / Hotel Management", "educations/0/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E0BAQFa3Yd2PfPzmg/company-logo_200_200/company-logo_200_200/0/1631320346714?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=s2A_W-U56Mg6Q3Hcewn8WsW6sbRkCzgzxuAhszHpt08", "educations/0/period/endedOn/month": "0", "educations/0/period/endedOn/year": "2008", "educations/0/period/startedOn/month": "0", "educations/0/period/startedOn/year": "2008", "educations/0/subtitle": "Bachelor's degree, KIP", "educations/0/title": "Assumption University", "educations/1/companyId": "10250", "educations/1/companyLink1": "https://www.li