"August 1, 2017", "recommendations/4/description": "Wail I was General Manager of the Vinpearl Golf-land Resort &Villas in Nha Trang, Khanh Hoa, Vietnam, \n\nMs Phuong Nguyen was our Director of Human Resource Management to which she controlled over 1,200 Associates one of Vietnam biggest Resorts. In this time I found her to be a hardworking Director in a very challenging position to which she did with no problem and was a great support to me and the whole management team  \n\nMs Nguyen main areas of work was to control the staff movements in a large Resort environment , Implementing the HR Management system and overall Plan for 2016/17 to which also included Associates & Management Develop plan of succession to which is very important part of Vinpearl Group HR. \n\nMs Nguyen was strong at her administration work and took care of not only the associates but also the Management Team and I enjoyed very much working with her & her team \n\nI am sure any Hotel or Company will have a great asset with her working with them and I wish her all the very best in the coming year \n\nYou are welcome to contact me any time for more information on Ms Phuong Nguyen\n\nBest Regards\n\nMarcel Sawyer \nGeneral Manager\n \n97 Renmin Road, Chancheng District,\nFoshan, Guangdong Province 528000, China\nE:  marcel.sawyere@marcopolohotels.com\n", "recommendations/4/name": "Jane Nguyen", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "HR professional | Executive Management | Hospitality &Real Estate Industry | Business Adminitration | SHRM | 15.000 followers", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/janenguyenhrd/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAsbbcAB396cBa1VacrXJEdR-UaCBGDCFWg", "recommendations/5/context": "Marcel  managed Erik directly", "recommendations/5/date": "March 25, 2017", "recommendations/5/description": "Wail I the GM and part of the Opening Team of Wanda Realm Dongying Erik was our DFB to which he did a great job to make Wanda a places to meet / eat / drink & party, his hard work and high service standards were clearly seen and this is why I promoted Erik to EAM to which I am sure he will be a great Hotel / General Manager one ", "recommendations/5/name": "Erik Sun", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "InterContinental Hotels & Resorts", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/erik-sun-0916aa76/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABAe1e0Bqi9Zpr0ayD02xY5tyhHGacskMCs", "recommendations/6/context": "Marcel  was senior to David but didn't manage David directly", "recommendations/6/date": "January 23, 2017", "recommendations/6/description": "A highly skilled hands-on hotel DOSM / EAM Sales with the unique capacity to multi-task various departments without breaking a sweat. David has been a mentor for me when it came to working in the hospitality industry by taking time to explain matters in a calm and easy-to-understand way for S&M. Especially his operational, HR, budget and financial knowledge in combination with his S&M - PR back-ground makes him the perfect hotelier for any property, whether big or small and would be a great support for any re branding or pre opening of hotels in Bangkok Thailand ", "recommendations/6/name": "David Holden", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Director", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/david-holden-a1108430/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAZq6K0B3uNK60OT6NdOrS9TA2yfPzNTbyc", "recommendations/7/context": "Marcel  managed Schulthess directly", "recommendations/7/date": "February 28, 2012", "recommendations/7/description": "As the Hotel Manager of Pathumwan Princess Chef Schulthess Flemming  was employed as the Executive Chef and was part of the team to Renovate the whole F&B operations to which he did with flying colors\nI would be happy to work again with Chef Flemming and would highly recommend him for any post as Chef or DFB \nIn you require any more information on Chef please contact me though here", "recommendations/7/name": "Schulthess Flemming", "recommendations/7/subtitle": "Executive Chef at Werkheim Uster", "recommendations/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/schulthess-flemming-a2b23a/", "recommendations/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAI1EMBlUmhloYkhOl2no1xIztPSvTotcw", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Timothy reported directly to Marcel ", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "September 12, 2023", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "It was my great pleasure to work with Marcel during his time with Marco Polo Lingnan Tiandi Foshan, China.  He is the type of leader that gives you trust and empowers you to make decision to solve problems.  A very professional individual who like to exceed all his objectives as well as to share his experience with his co-workers and employees.  In addition, Marcel is very well respected by colleagues as well as government officials in town as he always represents the hotel to participate CSR and government activities.  Marcel definitely is an asset for any employer.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Timothy Lai", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Leading Property Operations with Expertise in Staff Leadership and Brand Standards", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/timothylai2838/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAl33ngBq7OlnVw-j7uWahPcyEQ7pEWzTjY", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Jennifer managed Marcel  directly", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "August 4, 2023", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "It is a pleasure to introduce Marcel Sawyere, General Manager Marco Polo Foshan, with whom I worked for 5 years during my tenure as President.  Marcel is an entrepreneurially driven hotel leader, applying creative, ROI driven, resourceful solutions to challenges, such as the Private Dining experience for the hotel and ongoing cost-efficient renovation activities. He also embraces group initiatives and takes them to a new level, as was evident in his roll out of the 